The two days of matches feature the Seoul Dynasty, Hangzhou Spark, Guangzhou Charge, Shanghai Dragons, New York Excelsior, Chengdu Hunters, Philadelphia Fusion, Dallas Fuel, Los Angeles Valiant, Atlanta Reign, Houston Outlaws, San Francisco Shock, Philadelphia Fusion, Paris Eternal, Florida Mayhem, Boston Uprising, Toronto Defiant, and Los Angeles Gladiators. Who will come out on top between the Excelsior and the Dragons? Will the Fusion and Eternal go to a Map 5 for a third time in a row? Tune in!
